</node>
<node id="CRM">
  <data key="d0">CRM</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The CRM system tracks client commitments and Emergency Stock Requests, ensuring timely communication and escalation of delays.&lt;SEP&gt;CRM refers to the Customer Relationship Management system used to document resolutions for Level 2 complaints.&lt;SEP&gt;CRM (Customer Relationship Management) is a system used to log and manage client interactions and service requests.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35512f32ea45c1b275bccd44a565ae39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2d09e7ccd6006f073e3fa9c880cf01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd66dc6d321e6ab40161890d1bc0bc2c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779675856</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Watches">
  <data key="d0">Watches</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Watches are a product category managed under the supply chain, including perennial references and limited editions with specific allocation strategies.&lt;SEP&gt;Watches represent the dominant category in Australian revenue, accounting for 54% of total sales.&lt;SEP&gt;Watches are timekeeping devices that are part of a broader offering including jewellery, accessories, and fragrance.&lt;SEP&gt;Watches are categorized into perennial references and complications, with varying gross margins.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35512f32ea45c1b275bccd44a565ae39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-790cec48abbae1bcde2fc05c5a095bf6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4f5fe570c16349874515e195273ab1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779675899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Classic Jewellery">
  <data key="d0">Classic Jewellery</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Classic Jewellery includes items like LOVE, Trinity, and Juste un Clou, which are replenishment-driven with a dedicated safety stock.&lt;SEP&gt;Classic Jewellery includes items like LOVE and Trinity perennials, with a gross margin of 71–74%.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35512f32ea45c1b275bccd44a565ae39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779675899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="High Jewellery">
  <data key="d0">High Jewellery</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">High Jewellery refers to exclusive pieces allocated on a piece-by-piece basis, each tracked in the Aurelle master inventory system.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to unique or limited pieces in precious stones offered by Aurelle, representing the pinnacle of luxury.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to luxury items that perform above the average in the Asia-Pacific region within the Macau market.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to a category of luxury jewellery that contributes significantly to Aurelle's revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to luxury jewelry items that may be subject to complaints in the escalation protocol.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to a category of luxury items with a gross margin of 74–78%.&lt;SEP&gt;High Jewellery refers to the luxury segment of jewellery collections that represents the highest expression of craftsmanship and client relationship investment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35512f32ea45c1b275bccd44a565ae39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e887c12559193e3bccad1c5543198012&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b12fa9595ab8a07be0f25b056e92a77e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e119cc5bbc9fa38c53e731906650006&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2d09e7ccd6006f073e3fa9c880cf01f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54134887ae21d16b43d7cfa5f9280d3c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779675904</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fragrances &amp; Accessories">
  <data key="d0">Fragrances &amp; Accessories</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Fragrances and Accessories are managed separately from the jewellery and watches allocation policy through a commercial distribution network.&lt;SEP&gt;Fragrances &amp; Accessories are a product category with a gross margin of 58–63%.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-35512f32ea45c1b275bccd44a565ae39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1779675899</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Aurelle">
  <data key="d0">Aurelle</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Aurelle is a luxury brand renowned for its specialization in high-end jewelry and watchmaking, with a significant presence in the Southeast Asia, India, and Greater China markets. The brand is celebrated for its diverse collections, which feature both conceptual designs and iconic lines such as the Juste un Clou and Panthère collections. Aurelle places a strong emphasis on after-sales service and client care, viewing these elements as essential tools for enhancing consumer engagement and fostering lasting relationships.

In addition to its jewelry offerings, Aurelle is recognized for its luxury watches, which combine elegance with high-value timepieces. The brand's heritage and relevance in the Asia-Pacific (APAC) region are pivotal, as it strives to maintain a robust market presence and achieve ambitious revenue targets. Aurelle's strategic initiatives include a focus on client segmentation and relationship management, which are critical for driving significant revenue growth through retail and digitalization efforts.

Aurelle also organizes events aimed at enhancing client relationships and experiences within the APAC region. The brand operates boutiques that prioritize providing a unique client experience and high-quality service, further solidifying its commitment to luxury and customer satisfaction. Additionally, Aurelle is involved in retail pricing and financial policy in the APAC region, aligning its pricing strategies with a European headquarters model. Overall, Aurelle embodies a dedication to craftsmanship, quality, and the investment in client relationships across its various product lines.&lt;SEP&gt;Aurelle is the organization that developed the internal LLM used in the Gen AI Drafting Tool.&lt;SEP&gt;Aurelle is a company focused on human capital and talent strategy in the APAC region, emphasizing client relationships and employee roles.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a0504f98228375b771e952e83591e063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8dd643e5232ae7dacd9dfb7a9e9dd78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c58909936f746ddc15c50e77ba922597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e887c12559193e3bccad1c5543198012&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ec5de96956c14dd03345825280328af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc5ee76b42d06177ec4c2c2e85e1273d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-727ed2a5dcd62e44662faa62c9f70922&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b0093e976cf2a3869dc02b9a6e853&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-773da13c4ac946f97f5c614d22b9e04c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ab57f33730277bda03644a62ff087b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba5743a4090d85a22197f44e8ded1a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf98a52bede5692b73d05396929eb1d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54134887ae21d16b43d7cfa5f9280d3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7e8ab61cd77b5a3486de7c43c6b35e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7e1544435cdd5a7998e4cd7e79120db</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
