<node id="Australia">
  <data key="d0">Australia</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Australia is a country facing unique market challenges and opportunities within the Aurelle APAC portfolio.&lt;SEP&gt;Australia is a market that demonstrates steady-state premium market management with a focus on client retention.&lt;SEP&gt;Australia has the highest churn rate at 24%, characterized by a transactional market and lower emotional brand attachment.&lt;SEP&gt;Australia is projected to contribute USD 42M to Aurelle's revenue in FY2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Australia is a market with retail prices indexed at 108–112, which includes a GST of 10%.&lt;SEP&gt;Australia is a country noted for having a high client-facing turnover rate of 28% in the context of the text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-790cec48abbae1bcde2fc05c5a095bf6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8dd643e5232ae7dacd9dfb7a9e9dd78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b12fa9595ab8a07be0f25b056e92a77e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fded559bb9aca0f811af2eda90f8e432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1319dd867d0f1546d04a8c6700917538</data>
