  <data key="d2">Aurelle operates in Singapore, which serves as its APAC regional headquarters.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location with an internationally educated creative class, important for Aurelle's market presence.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is identified as the regional events hub for High Jewellery in the APAC region, specifically anchored at ION Orchard Maison Mansion.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a market with retail prices indexed at 104–107, characterized by a GST of 9%.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a city where the ION Orchard Maison Salon is located for high jewellery events.</data>
