  <data key="d2">Mumbai DLF Emporio serves as a flagship boutique in the Indian luxury market.&lt;SEP&gt;India is an emerging market for bridal jewelry, requiring education on G&lt;SEP&gt;India is classified as an 'Investment Market' for 2025, focusing on long-term market development with limited boutique networks in Delhi and Mumbai.&lt;SEP&gt;India is classified as an 'Investment Market' for Aurelle, with limited boutique presence and long-term development goals.&lt;SEP&gt;India is expected to generate USD 42M in revenue for Aurelle in FY2025.&lt;SEP&gt;India is a market with retail prices indexed at 120–130, noted for the highest duty burden in APAC.</data>
