<node id="Japan">
  <data key="d0">Japan</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Japan is a key market for Aurelle, particularly noted for high engagement ring spending.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan is a significant market for Aurelle, known for its high product knowledge and brand sensitivity among consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan has the lowest churn rate at 8% annually, attributed to a relationship culture and long stylist tenure.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan is a country in Northeast Asia known for its mature luxury market and high client loyalty metrics.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan is expected to contribute USD 85M to Aurelle's revenue in FY2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan is a market with retail prices indexed at 108–115, affected by a consumption tax.&lt;SEP&gt;Japan is a region where Aurelle APAC utilizes LINE as the primary CRM communication channel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c58909936f746ddc15c50e77ba922597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ec5de96956c14dd03345825280328af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fded559bb9aca0f811af2eda90f8e432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba5743a4090d85a22197f44e8ded1a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75d42a367a62c88ae3e50dd63478fd49</data>
