  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Hong Kong is a significant market for Aurelle's Panthère Motif Jewellery, appealing to Tier 1–2 clients.&lt;SEP&gt;Hong Kong serves as a sophisticated cross-border hub for luxury shopping and is a benchmark for retail excellence for Aurelle.&lt;SEP&gt;Hong Kong is a market with retail prices indexed at 103–106, characterized by a low duty environment.&lt;SEP&gt;Hong Kong is a city with a Landmark Maison for hosting high jewellery events.</data>
