  <data key="d0">Greater China</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Greater China encompasses Mainland China, Hong Kong, and Macau, which are key markets for Aurelle's brand strategy.&lt;SEP&gt;Greater China includes Mainland China, Hong Kong, and Macau, and is projected to generate USD 310M in revenue for Aurelle in FY2025.</data>
