<node id="South Korea">
  <data key="d0">South Korea</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">South Korea is an important market for Aurelle, characterized by younger affluent demographics and influencer-driven luxury discovery.&lt;SEP&gt;South Korea has an 11% churn rate, with strong brand loyalty influenced by cultural brand prestige.&lt;SEP&gt;South Korea is a rapidly growing market in Northeast Asia, influenced by cultural phenomena like K-drama and K-pop.&lt;SEP&gt;South Korea is projected to generate USD 62M in revenue for Aurelle in FY2025.&lt;SEP&gt;South Korea is a market with retail prices indexed at 110–116, which includes a luxury goods tax.&lt;SEP&gt;South Korea is a region where Aurelle APAC employs KakaoTalk as the primary communication tool.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ec5de96956c14dd03345825280328af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fded559bb9aca0f811af2eda90f8e432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba5743a4090d85a22197f44e8ded1a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b247997af40ea628c3c7b98ed0c14948&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75d42a367a62c88ae3e50dd63478fd49</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
