<node id="Southeast Asia">
  <data key="d0">Southeast Asia</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Southeast Asia includes countries like Singapore, Thailand, and the Philippines, where Aurelle aims to deepen its VIC network.&lt;SEP&gt;The Southeast Asia cluster, including Singapore, Thailand, Philippines, and Malaysia, is expected to contribute USD 93M in revenue for Aurelle in FY2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Southeast Asia is a region where email remains dominant for formal CRM communications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ec5de96956c14dd03345825280328af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e75dfca0f1f44ada8f07acdc5f6ea8c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75d42a367a62c88ae3e50dd63478fd49</data>
