<node id="LOVE Bracelet">
  <data key="d0">LOVE Bracelet</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The LOVE Bracelet is a product segment of Aurelle that is at risk from grey market price arbitrage.&lt;SEP&gt;The LOVE bracelet is a jewelry piece that has a strong cross-sell relationship with the Ballon Bleu watches.&lt;SEP&gt;The LOVE Bracelet is a luxury item that is less preferred compared to the Trinity Ring in the APAC market.&lt;SEP&gt;The LOVE Bracelet is a luxury item that is less preferred compared to the Trinity Ring in Taiwan.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7ec5de96956c14dd03345825280328af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f6b0093e976cf2a3869dc02b9a6e853&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92c4f747e6d7ccc5a653bbd427bff78f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba5743a4090d85a22197f44e8ded1a5</data>
