  <data key="d1">product</data>
  <data key="d2">Santos de Aurelle is an entry-level watch category that serves as part of Aurelle's client acquisition strategy.&lt;SEP&gt;Santos de Aurelle is a watch collection designed for male clients, known for its heritage and distinctive design features.&lt;SEP&gt;Santos de Aurelle is a watch model that generates top revenue volume for Aurelle.</data>
