<node id="Boutique Director">
  <data key="d0">Boutique Director</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">The Boutique Director also makes personal phone calls to Tier 1 Icon invitees as part of the invitation protocol.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boutique Director may personally call high-risk customers as part of a win-back campaign.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boutique Director oversees the operations and client interactions at the high jewellery events.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boutique Director is responsible for sending personal thank-you notes to preview attendees and overseeing boutique operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Boutique Director is accountable for the boutique's performance, managing staff and client experiences.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-02eefa7f22ecbf190aa8b142a4701ff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fded559bb9aca0f811af2eda90f8e432&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-141486b564589360e8df069f117681fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54134887ae21d16b43d7cfa5f9280d3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7e1544435cdd5a7998e4cd7e79120db</data>
