  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Mystery Shopping involves unannounced visits to evaluate boutique performance against established standards.&lt;SEP&gt;Mystery shopping involves unannounced visits to boutiques to evaluate service quality, conducted by a regional operations team or approved third-party firm.</data>
