  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A Performance Improvement Plan is triggered for boutiques scoring below 75 on mystery shopping, requiring action within a 60-day timeline.&lt;SEP&gt;Performance Improvement Plan is a corrective action triggered when a boutique scores below the minimum acceptable mystery shop score.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf98a52bede5692b73d05396929eb1d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2d09e7ccd6006f073e3fa9c880cf01f</data>
